00:03:25.150 --> 00:03:27.940
It's what we've adopted
as our house style.

00:03:27.940 --> 00:03:31.100
It's how we fashion
our icons within Aqua.

00:03:31.480 --> 00:03:36.200
In emotive icons,
we'll be looking at icons that express

00:03:36.620 --> 00:03:40.100
Something beyond the symbol,
the basic symbol.

00:03:40.130 --> 00:03:43.700
Icons for the first time
can express feeling.

00:03:43.890 --> 00:03:47.910
In genres, we'll be looking at a
new concept for Mac OS X,

00:03:47.910 --> 00:03:52.960
