which is reinforced by that glyph on top.

00:35:39.320 --> 00:35:44.610
So we study a lot of real world objects.

00:35:47.230 --> 00:35:50.520
It's a bit of a quick
walkthrough on certain things,

00:35:50.520 --> 00:35:56.540
but I guess the idea that we'd
like to get across is that

00:35:59.000 --> 00:36:05.880
A lot of attention is paid to
items in the Aqua Icon family.

00:36:05.880 --> 00:36:11.740
We spend a lot of time on these things
